- Go to contest: CodeForces Div 2 or AtCoder Beginer
- The contest in given time
- Once finished, go to problems not solved and read editorial
- If the problem contains topic you don't know, search it up in handbook
- After reading handbook, solve sample problems at: https://www.quora.com/What-is-a-list-of-data-structures-that-a-competitive-programmer-must-know/answer/Sameer-Gulati-3?ch=10&share=dcc3b398&srid=oeMh
- After practicing on that concept, return to the contest problem and try to solve it
- If the problems look too hard, skip them
- PARTICIPATE IN THE CONTESTS!!! DON'T BE AFRAID TO FAIL
